library_management/
│
├── sql/
│   └── schema.sql                  ← CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS schema script
│
├── app/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── bootstrap.py                ← DB init + first-run seed data
│   ├── database.py                 ← Connection singleton, runs schema.sql
│   ├── dal.py                      ← All raw SQL queries
│   ├── dto.py                      ← Dataclasses (MemberDTO, BookDTO, etc.)
│   └── business_logic.py           ← Business rules & recommendation engine
│   └── validation/
│       ├── __init__.py
│       ├── errors.py
│       ├── rules.py
│       ├── member_validator.py
│       ├── book_validator.py
│       └── loan_validator.py
│
├── gui/
│   ├── assets/                     ← images, icons (e.g. menu_bg_image.png)
│   ├── MainTkWindow.py             ← Root Tk() window, frame router
│   ├── SideBar_Menu.py             ← Left sidebar, always visible
│   ├── Dashboard_Page.py           ← KPIs + area chart + recent loans table
│   ├── Books_Page.py               ← Book catalogue, search, action buttons
│   ├── Categories_Page.py          ← Add/delete category (embedded frame)
│   ├── Book_Edit_Page.py           ← Add/edit book form (embedded frame)
│   ├── Loans_Page.py               ← Search, borrow, return action
│   ├── Rating_Page.py              ← 5-star rating (embedded frame, post-return)
│   ├── Members_Page.py             ← Member form + list table
│   ├── Recommend_Page.py           ← Book recommendations (embedded frame)
│   └── Statistics_Page.py          ← Charts + loan history table
│
└── main.py                         ← Entry point, calls bootstrap then launches GUI
